WEBVTT

00:07.859 --> 00:13.822
Riots start in the Tottenham section of London, after a man dies in a police shootout.

00:22.363 --> 00:25.751
Violence spreads to other parts of the British capital.

00:33.761 --> 00:38.303
Manchester, Birmingham and other English cities are also hit.

00:44.381 --> 00:47.358
Extra police are called in to restore calm.

00:55.011 --> 00:58.426
British politicians inspect the riot damage.

